import React from 'react' import { Link } from 'react-router-dom' export default function Contact(props) { let CompanyDetails = []; if(props.getCompanyDetails) { props.getCompanyDetails.map((value, key) => ( CompanyDetails['CompanyName'] = value.companyName, CompanyDetails['CompanyAddress'] = value.companyAddress, CompanyDetails['CompanyAddressLink'] = value.companyAddressLink, CompanyDetails['CompanyPhone'] = value.companyPhone, CompanyDetails['CompanyFacebook'] = value.companyFacebook, CompanyDetails['CompanyTwitter'] = value.companyTwitter, CompanyDetails['CompanyInstagram'] = value.companyInstagram, CompanyDetails['CompanyLinkedin'] = value.companyLinkedin )); } return ( <>
Home   /   Contact

Contact Us

Contact Info

  • {CompanyDetails['CompanyAddress']}
  • {CompanyDetails['CompanyPhone']}
  • {CompanyDetails['CompanyFacebook']}
) }
